TopicTitle: Infrequent crashes when transitioning from VAB to Launch Pad

Articles.Content:
Version: 0.24.2 32-bit KSP

System: Windows 8

What Happens: KSP infrequently crashes, usually when transitioning from VAB to Launch Pad, but happened once while I was controlling a spacecraft. Game is not completely unplayable as the crash doesn't happen every time, just some of the time.

[EDIT] Crashes have now spread to selecting parts in the VAB/SPH, during flight and when transitioning to the Launch Pad from KSC.

Steps to replicate: Unfortunately don't know. I installed all the mods in one go but otherwise have no problems.
